Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.32,0:00:03.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Rock away your existence,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.69,0:00:06.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shouting that you are here…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.57,0:00:12.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A new journey begins now.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.03,0:00:28.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,As we survived through\Nthe changing seasons,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.99,0:00:34.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,we gained knowledge and strength,\N(just looks like a survival game)
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.53,0:00:37.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But the forgotten memories,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.15,0:00:40.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,of the feelings abandoned within\Nthe flows of time,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.69,0:00:45.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,have also been lost.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.69,0:00:51.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,When sinking down,\Nwe learned loneliness.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.20,0:00:56.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But now we’ve met each other,\Nwe are no longer alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.78,0:01:02.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Unveil your feelings,\NThose high emotions
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.40,0:01:07.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Those tears will change your fate.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.69,0:01:10.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Pound your heartbeat\Nagainst the darkness,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.86,0:01:19.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We’re sure to meet,\NUnder the same flag of pain
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.15,0:01:48.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mystery of the Targeted Merchants
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.03,0:01:56.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Did they really come this way?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.07,0:01:58.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But why come this way?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.15,0:02:02.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They shouldn’t come this way\Nif it’s as you say, Choji.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.95,0:02:06.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I said that because I didn’t think\Nwe were being targeted.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.45,0:02:09.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don’t think this is\Nthe time to argue…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.28,0:02:12.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We have to formulate\Nsome sort of strategy.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.45,0:02:14.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You say that, but…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.45,0:02:15.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.32,0:02:18.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Have the guys\Nyou spoke of caught up?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.40,0:02:23.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then we should divide up\Nthis group in two.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.24,0:02:26.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Here it’s hard enough\Nto protect one.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.69,0:02:28.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What’s the point of dividing\N the group in two?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.69,0:02:29.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,N-Naruto!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.86,0:02:34.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Please, tell us what your idea is.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.95,0:02:37.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is what I mean.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.28,0:02:39.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,For example…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.03,0:02:45.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let’s say there are\N ten persimmons here.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.69,0:02:48.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is anything okay\Nif it’s a food?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.69,0:02:50.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.69,0:02:53.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then I want it to be ramen!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.28,0:02:56.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Naruto, it’s an example, so…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.95,0:02:58.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then we’ll make it ramen.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.11,0:03:01.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Someone is after\Nthese ten bowls of ramen.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.65,0:03:04.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And there are three people\N to protect the ramen.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.53,0:03:08.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And so one person has\Nto protect roughly three bowls.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.90,0:03:10.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, no. If it’s ramen,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.40,0:03:12.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,we should just eat it all\Nbefore they come.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.90,0:03:14.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That would settle things.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.03,0:03:21.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,N-Naruto. This ramen is\Nfor delivery to someone,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.69,0:03:22.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,so we can’t eat it.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.07,0:03:26.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Really? But the ramen\Nwon’t be tasty if it gets soggy.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.82,0:03:28.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I’m moving on.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.69,0:03:31.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If three people protect\Nten bowls of ramen,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.86,0:03:33.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,one person protects\Nabout three bowls.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.28,0:03:36.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But this ramen has\Nlegs for escaping.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.90,0:03:39.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ramen with legs for escaping?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.74,0:03:42.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Five bowls of ramen\Nquick to escape…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.20,0:03:48.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and five bowls of ramen\Nslow to escape.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.40,0:03:51.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Right, right..\NThings are kind of getting crazy.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.69,0:03:54.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I see. If we divide them\Ninto two groups…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.86,0:03:58.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Of course, the pursuers would target\Nthe group that is slow to escape first.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.20,0:04:02.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So we have one person\N defend the preceding group
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.69,0:04:05.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and two people\Nfor the group that is slow to escape.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.74,0:04:06.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Right, right.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.74,0:04:11.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,By doing this, as for protecting\N the slow group,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.07,0:04:13.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,now one person can just protect\Ntwo and a half bowls.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.69,0:04:16.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.61,0:04:20.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In other words, the ramen that are\Nquick to escape are the young people
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.20,0:04:24.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and the ramen that are slow to escape\Nare the elderly people and children, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.65,0:04:26.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Exactly.\NNot only will the possibility of
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.69,0:04:28.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,the former to completely\Nget away increase,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.69,0:04:30.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,the burden on the latter\Nto protect will decrease.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.69,0:04:32.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It’s a strategy that kills two birds\N with one stone.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.69,0:04:36.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You’re smart.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.82,0:04:39.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,However…\Nthe elderly people and children will…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.69,0:04:43.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I just stated a rational idea.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.61,0:04:44.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There’s the possibility
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.74,0:04:46.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,of complete annihilation\Nif we stay in a group.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.69,0:04:47.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Am I wrong, Yurinoshin?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.49,0:04:49.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.69,0:04:53.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then it’s settled.\NLet’s divide everyone up in two.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.24,0:04:56.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I’m sorry, gramps.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.69,0:04:59.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don’t worry about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.69,0:05:03.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It would be trouble if something bad\Nwere to happen to the men in their prime.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.74,0:05:07.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You’ve got a wife and kid\Nat home, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.61,0:05:12.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then we’ll be going on\Nahead first, Naruto, Choji.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.32,0:05:14.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Right.\NWe’re counting on you, Hinata.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.32,0:05:18.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Naruto and I will deal\Nwith the pursuers.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.69,0:05:20.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Right.\NI’ll protect them well.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.69,0:05:32.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Lady Haruna.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.69,0:05:36.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yurinoshin, keep your mouth shut.\NWhat’s your mission?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.32,0:05:39.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is it not to protect me?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.11,0:05:42.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Things will be settled if Kikusuke\Ndefeats those guys.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.90,0:05:46.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then shall we get going, too?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.65,0:05:49.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I’m counting on you, Brother Choji.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.78,0:05:52.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Right! 					Leave it to me!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.36,0:05:52.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Choji.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.07,0:05:55.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You go on ahead.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.07,0:05:56.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.90,0:06:01.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I’m going back to check things out\Nat the place where the traps are.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.69,0:06:04.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But if you do that, you may encounter\N the pursuers along the way…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.53,0:06:05.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That’s fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.90,0:06:09.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Doing something like waiting\N to be attacked isn’t my style!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.90,0:06:10.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Naruto!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.78,0:06:13.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Leave it to me!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.65,0:06:15.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I meant…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.11,0:06:17.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There’s no point to our strategy
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.69,0:06:19.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,if I have to protect five people\N by myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.86,0:06:21.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Right, there’s no point.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.20,0:06:29.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We came down that path,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.70,0:06:31.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,so the trap should be\Nup ahead somewhere.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.83,0:06:34.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I guess I’ll take a shortcut!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.74,0:06:51.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What’s this? 					What happened?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.65,0:06:56.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why is it so wet?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.40,0:07:09.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What’re these wounds?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.65,0:07:14.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This guy’s…!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.65,0:07:25.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you serious?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.11,0:07:29.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is something wrong, Brother Choji?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.70,0:07:31.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.69,0:07:33.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I see…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.24,0:07:35.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I feel it.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.69,0:07:38.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Even I can sense this much bloodlust.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.61,0:07:39.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It’s close now.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.69,0:07:42.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.99,0:07:44.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Rain?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.99,0:07:49.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is the worst. Rain wipes out\Nall presence of the enemy.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.69,0:07:54.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.95,0:07:56.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This rain is weird.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.32,0:08:04.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Gather around, everyone!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.07,0:08:10.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Stay close to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.36,0:08:13.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What’s…this?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.69,0:08:20.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is bad!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.57,0:08:23.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What was that now?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.69,0:08:26.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Everyone! Get under the cart!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.57,0:08:28.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We’re already under here!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.69,0:08:30.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You’re quick!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.07,0:08:32.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Choji!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.69,0:08:34.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Naruto!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.65,0:08:37.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Get down!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.86,0:08:39.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shadow Clone Jutsu!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.69,0:09:00.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Naruto! Could you say so\Nat the start
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.57,0:09:02.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,if you’re going to\Nuse paper bombs?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.69,0:09:07.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All right. It seems they’re gone.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.90,0:09:09.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why did they disappear?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.49,0:09:12.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Isn’t it obvious?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.86,0:09:15.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They have no business with a shop\Nthat doesn’t have the thing they want.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.07,0:09:17.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thing they want?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.69,0:09:18.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That’s right.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.86,0:09:21.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If a shop’s sold out\Nof the item you want,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.32,0:09:23.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,you’d go to another shop, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.69,0:09:28.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Could it be that the thing that he wants\Nis in the other group?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.24,0:09:31.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What does that mean?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.49,0:09:34.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hinata’s in danger!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.11,0:09:38.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Everyone, leave your stuff here\Nand take only what you need!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.08,0:09:40.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hinata is?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.69,0:09:53.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Everyone, we’ll put up our tents here\N for today and rest.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.40,0:09:57.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It’s dangerous to move in the dark.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.57,0:10:08.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.15,0:10:13.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We finally caught up.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.36,0:10:19.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Naruto, Choji. What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.69,0:10:23.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,“What is it,” nothing.\NThe situation has changed.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.28,0:10:26.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It seems someone among\Nthese people
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.69,0:10:28.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,is hiding something important.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.69,0:10:31.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Something important?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.28,0:10:36.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It should probably have something\Nto do with us being chased.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.70,0:10:41.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But who is hiding what?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.78,0:10:45.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It’s most likely you guys,\NShun and Yurinoshin.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.53,0:10:49.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don’t be silly!\NWhat’re you saying we’re hiding?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.28,0:10:50.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don’t play innocent!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.20,0:10:54.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kikusuke has been killed\Nby someone!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.45,0:10:56.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.65,0:10:57.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kikusuke was?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.28,0:11:01.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don’t play innocent!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.28,0:11:05.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kikusuke has been killed\Nby someone!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.61,0:11:07.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.69,0:11:08.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kikusuke was?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.49,0:11:11.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why should he have to\Nsuit up like a Shinobi,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.45,0:11:14.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,fight those guys and then get killed?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.11,0:11:17.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It’s not necessary to tell you guys.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.82,0:11:20.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But if that’s why we’re being chased…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.69,0:11:23.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It means you guys are putting\Neveryone in danger.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.61,0:11:26.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you don’t tell us honestly,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.40,0:11:28.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,we won’t be able to protect\N even what we can protect.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.69,0:11:30.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kikunojou…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.28,0:11:35.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kikunojou?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.95,0:11:38.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You mean Kikusuke?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.53,0:11:42.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes… And my name isn’t Yurinoshin.\N It’s Yurinojou.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.69,0:11:44.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Stop, Yurinojou!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.86,0:11:49.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The person here is Lady Haruna,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.69,0:11:53.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,the only daughter of the feudal lord\Nof the Land of Greens.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.90,0:11:55.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Princess?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.78,0:12:00.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Princess Haruna of the Land of Greens.\NYou’ve grown up so much…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.45,0:12:03.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,P-Princess…?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.99,0:12:05.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You were a woman?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.82,0:12:09.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Lady Haruna,\Nit is as these people say.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.07,0:12:13.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We must not put everyone in danger\Nby hiding the truth any further.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.20,0:12:21.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But why is someone like a princess\N mingling among merchants?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.74,0:12:25.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There was information of\Na coup in the Land of Greens.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.24,0:12:27.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A coup?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.78,0:12:32.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The Land of Greens was a small,\Nbut calm and peaceful land.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.69,0:12:35.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,However, it was by no means\Na prosperous land.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.90,0:12:38.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Before we realized it,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.45,0:12:40.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,more than half of the public officials\N had been bought off.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.53,0:12:43.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Who in the world would do that…?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.99,0:12:46.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The ringleaders are three brothers\Ncalled the Janin,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.86,0:12:48.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,evil Ninja who came from\N across the sea.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.69,0:12:50.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Janin?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.95,0:12:53.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes. They’re guys who use\Na particular type of Ninjutsu
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.49,0:12:56.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and are called as such\Nbecause of their frightfulness.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.40,0:13:02.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They’ve taken many lives\Nand think nothing of it
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.32,0:13:04.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,if it’s for their own gains.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.36,0:13:07.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They treat people like worms…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.40,0:13:11.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But why the Land of Greens?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.08,0:13:13.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don’t know why.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.57,0:13:18.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But his lordship had Lady Haruna\Nhide amongst a group of merchants
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.70,0:13:20.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and got her out of the land.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.53,0:13:25.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kikunojou and I were left\Nwith the protection of the princess,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.40,0:13:26.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but we were insecure with\Njust the two of us.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.69,0:13:31.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So then we hurriedly commissioned\Nthe Hidden Leaf
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.20,0:13:33.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,under the pretext of protection\Nfrom bandits.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.32,0:13:36.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why didn’t you tell us\N something that important?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.07,0:13:40.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There’s no way I could have.\NMy escape is top secret.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.65,0:13:42.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Besides, what would happen\N if I were to have told you?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.99,0:13:45.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The end result would’ve been\N you guys running away in confusion.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.69,0:13:48.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No way would I do something\N like run away.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.78,0:13:51.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kikunojou might not have\Nhad to die if
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.15,0:13:54.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,we had understood the situation\N from the start.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.69,0:13:55.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I wonder.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.24,0:14:00.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,One of you guys might’ve ended up\Nlike Kikunojou.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.69,0:14:04.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We’re actually fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.45,0:14:07.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But to think you’d go so far as to involve\Nthe old lady and the children.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.78,0:14:09.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It couldn’t be!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.69,0:14:11.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Were you intending to use\N the old lady and the kids as decoys
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.78,0:14:13.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and escape just yourself?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.11,0:14:16.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That’s right. What of it?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.36,0:14:19.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Choji! Hinata!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.69,0:14:24.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,As for me,\NI’m really tickedoff right now!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.69,0:14:26.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So what of it?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.45,0:14:29.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If something should happen\N in the land,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.28,0:14:31.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I would become\Nthe only blood relative
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.07,0:14:33.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,of the feudal lord of\N the Land of Greens.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.74,0:14:36.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If I can just survive,\Nthings could be restored someday,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.65,0:14:39.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,even if the Land of Greens\Nwere to be destroyed.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.69,0:14:45.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Say what?! Just what is it\Nyou think of people’s lives?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.69,0:14:58.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Please forgive her.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.11,0:15:00.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yurinojou.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.61,0:15:05.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is it not your mission to protect me?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.53,0:15:07.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You’re still talking about such things…?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.69,0:15:10.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Please wait, Naruto!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.69,0:15:14.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Lady Haruna, that’s true for me.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.69,0:15:16.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,However, these people are different.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.36,0:15:20.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The mission they undertook\Nwas to protect merchants.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.78,0:15:22.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It was not to protect us.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.28,0:15:27.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Indeed, what we heard about
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.65,0:15:30.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,was a D-rank mission to protect\Nall of the merchants.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.86,0:15:35.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Protecting a prominent figure of\Na land is an A-rank mission.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.49,0:15:38.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The rank differs by far too much.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.07,0:15:41.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you guys saying\Nyou’re going to forsake me?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.15,0:15:44.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Weren’t you saying until just now
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.07,0:15:46.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,that you didn’t trust people like us?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.69,0:15:48.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I’ll protect you with my life,\NLady Haruna…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.03,0:15:52.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shut up, Yurinojou!\NKikunojou was your senior disciple.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.70,0:15:54.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There’s no way you alone\Ncould defeat an opponent
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.69,0:15:56.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,whom he couldn’t defeat!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.24,0:16:02.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That will just be our destiny\Nwhen that happens, Lady Haruna.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.20,0:16:14.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Watch, Brother Choji.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.95,0:16:19.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh! Awesome, awesome.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.49,0:16:22.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I’m sorry about earlier.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.53,0:16:25.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It happened so suddenly,\NI couldn’t stop.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.24,0:16:28.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don’t be concerned about me.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.61,0:16:32.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,However, please forgive Lady Haruna.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.95,0:16:35.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The Land of Greens is a small land.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.70,0:16:38.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,For the sake of the land’s survival,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.69,0:16:41.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Lady Haruna was kept under\N the custody of another land,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.69,0:16:44.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,as a hostage all by herself\Nsince she was little.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.69,0:16:45.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hostage?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.57,0:16:50.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It frequently happens in\Na small land in a war-torn world.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.74,0:16:55.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,When Lady Haruna returned\N from the other land,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.28,0:16:57.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,she had completely lost her feelings\Nof trust towards people.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.69,0:17:03.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Lady Haruna is also\Na victim of a turbulent world.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.20,0:17:08.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There’s a village
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.61,0:17:10.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,about one league down\N the mountain from here.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.86,0:17:11.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,For the time being,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.74,0:17:14.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,we’ll leave the old woman\N and the others there.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.03,0:17:16.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Be careful now.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.78,0:17:17.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You guys, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.74,0:17:19.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Bye!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.69,0:17:22.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why are you separating them from us?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.36,0:17:25.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They still have value for\Nmy personal use.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.07,0:17:28.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you still going on about that?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.45,0:17:32.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They went so far as to discard\N their merchandise for your sake.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.11,0:17:35.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then we should also leave this place.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.95,0:17:36.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We must not.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.57,0:17:39.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If we go into hiding,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.36,0:17:41.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,there’s a possibility of\Nthat group being attacked again.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.82,0:17:47.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Exactly. This time,\Nit’s our turn to be the decoy
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.69,0:17:48.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,in order to protect them.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.78,0:17:51.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Do as you like!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.86,0:18:09.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hinata, I’ll take care of things here.\NPlease rest a while.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.15,0:18:12.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, do that.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.40,0:18:14.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Th-Then, if you insist.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.70,0:18:31.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, yeah. Here.\NKikunojou was holding this.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.45,0:18:34.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks, Naruto.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.11,0:18:40.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kikunojou was a master\Nof the Flower Ninjutsu
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.86,0:18:41.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,passed down in the Land of Greens.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.07,0:18:45.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We learned together\N when we were little
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.49,0:18:47.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and I couldn’t beat him even once…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.82,0:18:52.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now I have forever lost\N the chance to beat him.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.32,0:18:55.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No… You still have a chance.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.11,0:18:56.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.12,0:19:01.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you beat the guy\Nwho defeated Kikunojou,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.15,0:19:03.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,you will have beaten Kikunojou!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.28,0:19:06.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Naruto… You’re exactly right…!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.28,0:19:07.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Here they come!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.07,0:19:11.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Other than the fact that\Nthe enemy uses water,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.69,0:19:13.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,we have absolutely no idea\Nwhat they’ll come at us with.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.70,0:19:15.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I know.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.20,0:19:19.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Go! Flower Ninja Art:!\NFlying Flowers: Falling Foliage.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.69,0:19:32.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.86,0:19:35.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He changed the trajectory in mid-air?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.69,0:19:41.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, no!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.20,0:19:44.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I finally got you!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.95,0:19:47.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Gotcha.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.57,0:19:50.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,To think you’d\Nmake me look like a fool.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.86,0:19:53.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So you finally show yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.61,0:19:56.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I will avenge Kikunojou!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.90,0:19:59.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Try it if you can.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.28,0:20:07.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I won’t let you get away!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.78,0:20:19.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Too bad. You’re one person short.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.45,0:20:22.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I’ve set a share for one more.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.49,0:20:26.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don’t know about that.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.24,0:20:43.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,First, I’ll take care of you, boy.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.53,0:20:45.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Water Style: Liquid Memory!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.69,0:20:50.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Naruto…!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.07,0:20:53.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And this!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.86,0:20:57.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Summoning Jutsu!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.78,0:21:03.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.65,0:21:04.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is that…?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.69,0:21:07.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The Jutsu that killed Kikunojou?!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.99,0:21:12.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Vanish and die!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.69,0:21:30.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yesterday’s Call Sign,\Nwas all from my cell phone.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.40,0:21:37.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In a strange park,\NI play the Fuzz Guitar without enthusiasm.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.28,0:21:52.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yellow Moon.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.78,0:21:59.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Even now, counting to three,\NI open my eyes
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.69,0:22:04.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shadow Moon I am still dreaming.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.86,0:22:11.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Look at my eyes, look at my eyes,\Nas we face one another’s back
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.78,0:22:18.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Look at my eyes, when can we meet?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.69,0:22:25.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,EveryDay EveryNight\NWith every word I can think of
Dialogue: 0,0:22:25.61,0:22:32.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Right away, my messy feelings as is,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:33.95,0:22:38.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A magical chord change, in a restless city
Dialogue: 0,0:22:40.74,0:22:45.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A daily JAZZ Guitar played\Nin a soft minor key
Dialogue: 0,0:22:52.69,0:22:54.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What is this huge thing?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:54.20,0:22:55.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don’t wanna become its food.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:55.95,0:22:57.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let me tell you one thing.\NI’m not tasty.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.78,0:22:58.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I’m not tasty, either.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:58.99,0:23:00.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But Choji would be more\Nworthwhile to eat.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:00.65,0:23:02.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, Naruto would be tastier.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.69,0:23:04.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Be eaten for the sake of your comrade.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:04.11,0:23:05.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You’re the one who will\Nbecome it food.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:05.69,0:23:07.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This isn’t the time to be arguing\N about stuff like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:07.61,0:23:09.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yurinojou!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:10.11,0:23:12.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Anyway, we just have to run\Nwith all our might for now!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:13.53,0:23:16.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Next time:\N“A Limitless Supply of Ninja Tools”
